{"tid":1385764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[護航] 放工全民airdrop護航大法","createTime":"2019-07-30T07:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T10:54:13.000Z","uid":187796,"like":154,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"d78fce649193cb4500e3c1cb72a7a90232f5c3a9","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:08:30.000Z","msg":"今朝有唔少人係港鐵搞不合作運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好問有冇用住，既然搞左，就算有冇用都要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全力護航</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將呢件事嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">效益最大化</span></span>！！<br />\n<br />\n所以要趁今朝燥底嘅人放工咁開心，再黎一個回馬槍<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全力文宣！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話比佢地知我地嘅原意，補足番<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今朝解釋唔夠</span></span>嘅缺陷！<br />\n<br />\n番緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔得閒整文宣，但我覺得只要<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大大隻字寫句對唔住係張圖中間，等人地preview個陣睇到</span></span>就係最吸引到嘅地方。<br />\nSomething like that:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j5p0CYz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj5p0CYz.png&h=f653bb76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tiJMywV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtiJMywV.png&h=98d9a158&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">事出突然，幫手推到放工嘅朋友睇到一齊drop!</span></span><br />\n//我時常提醒自己：政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。//"},{"pid":"100ef799de467da205e23a5be21a5a2d47148882","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46bcfe6696388962c9b556a6d24fc99e0dcef7e5","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65b61188a59bc0622e961270819fa7fd8d6f6675","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ed97a39806bf1ae211bef5bd5052ae49e440abc","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:10:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"130c5aa6eece73f0a0b7b2ed7af9882dc41b5e33","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />射唔到波"},{"pid":"b3b2e4bfc328cd4439166c131921ada4c2103b53","tid":1385764,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:11:01.000Z","msg":"夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"cf49462a0d756f00566b3b6b999aeb3f3b7b1e92","tid":1385764,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1af92222a046a77faf83d3569af6083e0b9e9c6","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n放工前要睇到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6627ee5049246a5710fc1374e6ae926d9c809ed5","tid":1385764,"uid":61292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"751f171ff223503d71702e9dc0c00edcb5f80470","tid":1385764,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:13:28.000Z","m